messageBody:
Hi all.
I'm new in this group and I'm starting research thesis on multi-
agent testing.
I would greatly appreciate any information on this area. Any ideas
on research directions and/or references would be greatly
appreciated especially on automatic test cases generation for black
box testing.
Thank you,
Yacine
